&lt;p&gt;The women&#39;s service is looking to recruit to the newly created post of Deputy Divisional Director of Midwifery, Gynaecology and Sexual Health.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;br /&gt;The Care Group is looking for an exceptional leader to provide operational guidance and leadership to the nursing and midwifery teams.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;br /&gt;The role will involve supporting the care group teams to maximise their performance against key local and national targets whilst enhancing patient care.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;br /&gt;The post holder will be a key member of the operational care group teams working with the matrons, care group manager and Clinical Director&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;br /&gt;supported by the Divisional Director of Midwifery, Gynaecology and Sexual Health and the wider Divisional Team of Five.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;For further details / informal visits contact:&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;NameCarla Jones-CharlesJob titleDivisional Director of Midwifery, Gynaecology and Sexual Health.Email addresscarla.jones-charles@walsallhealthcare.nhs.uk&lt;/p&gt;
